TextEng: Me not who you think. You got me mixed up with some other one.
Text: 나 네가 생각하는 사람 아냐. 다른 사람이랑 헷갈린 거야.

TextEng: No, I think you have me confused with someone else.
Text: 아니, 날 다른 사람으로 착각한 것 같은데.

TextEng: Yes, me be <FullName>.
Yes, I am <FullName>.
Me not care 'bout honor! Me only here cause me want to get lots of gold and magic stuff!
Text: 나 명예 같은 거 관심 없어! 금이랑 마법 물건 많이 갖고 싶어서 온 거야!

TextEng: Me got lots of talent. Me used to honors like this by now.
Text: 나 재능 많아. 이런 명예는 이제 익숙해.

TextEng: It be a big honor for me to serve Neverwinter.
Who cares about honor? I just came because I sense the potential for real profit.
Text: 명예가 뭐가 중요해? 난 돈이 될 것 같아서 온 거야.

TextEng: Me not really interested in talking at you.
Tell me 'bout you brother.
What you mean 'bout guards not keeping order?
Text: 경비들이 질서를 못 지킨다는 게 무슨 말이야?

TextEng: Me not actually know much 'bout plague.
Text: 나 역병에 대해서는 사실 잘 몰라.

TextEng: I'm not really interested in chatting with you.
Text: 너랑 잡담하는 건 별로 관심 없어.

TextEng: Tell me about your brother.
What did you mean about the city guard barely able to keep order?
Text: 경비대가 겨우 질서를 유지한다는 게 무슨 말이야?

TextEng: I don't actually know that much about the plague.
Me not care 'bout this. Me want to go now.
Text: 나 이거 관심 없어. 이제 갈래.

TextEng: Sound like whole city be in big trouble.
Text: 도시 전체가 큰 문제인 것 같네.

TextEng: You not got cleric or priest who can help?
Text: 도와줄 수 있는 성직자나 사제는 없어?

TextEng: There be somebody who look for cure?
Great story. I'll be going now.
Sounds like the whole city is doomed.
Can't the clerics and priests do anything to help?
Shouldn't someone be looking for a cure?
Text: 누군가 치료제를 찾아야 하는 거 아냐?

TextEng: Me want go now.
You know more 'bout cure rumors?
You got other stuff you tell me 'bout plague?
Text: 역병에 대해 다른 거 더 말해줄 수 있어?

TextEng: I think it's time for me to go now.
Do you know anything more about these rumors of a cure?
Text: 치료제 소문에 대해 더 아는 거 있어?

TextEng: Can you tell me anything else about this plague?
Text: 이 역병에 대해 다른 거 더 말해줄 수 있어?

TextEng: When you have as much talent and skill as I do you get used to these kind of honors.
Text: 나처럼 재능과 실력이 있으면 이런 명예에는 익숙해지지.

TextEng: It is both an honor and a privilege for me to serve Neverwinter.
Goodbye.
Me want ask questions.
I want to ask you some more questions.
Anything else?
What you know 'bout rumors of plague cure?
Text: 역병 치료제 소문에 대해 뭐 알아?

TextEng: You tell more 'bout plague.
Anything else you can tell me?
Text: 다른 거 더 말해줄 수 있어?

TextEng: Tell me more about these rumors of a plague cure.
Text: 역병 치료제 소문에 대해 더 말해줘.

TextEng: Tell me more about the Wailing Death.
